title: Binance discontinues Visa Debit Card in email sent to clients
description: In an email sent to Binance clients, the world’s largest exchange shares that the Binance Visa Debit card will not be available from December 2023 onwards.

title: Solana gaining momentum according to Nansen report
description: Following FTX's collapse, Nansen on-chain data shows that SOL has outperformed ETH, emerging as the preferred investment choice.
